{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Immerse Yourself in Japan\u2019s Hot Springs (Onsen), Create Your Own Garden, Nurture Pets &amp; Fish, and Enjoy Relaxing Mini-Games</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the serene world of <strong>Onsen</strong>, where the warm embrace of Japanese hot springs meets the ultimate idle simulation experience. Find peace and relaxation as you create your own slice of paradise, while also connecting with others. Enjoy a seamless blend of idle relaxation and engaging activities, perfectly balancing your downtime. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Create Your Dream Garden</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Design and decorate your very own fish pond garden, with a variety of ornaments to choose from, bringing life and color to your peaceful retreat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401730/extras/deco.gif?t=1731790153\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Engaging Mini-Games</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take a break and unwind with charming mini-games like gardening, cooking, and firefly catching, each offering a delightful twist to your idle experience while earning you in-game currency to purchase more items.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401730/extras/cooking.gif?t=1731790153\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401730/extras/firefly.gif?t=1731790153\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Character Creation </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401730/extras/avatar.gif?t=1731790153\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Raise Adorable Cats</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Foster and interact with cute cats, adding warmth and joy to your onsen sanctuary.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401730/extras/pets.gif?t=1731790153\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Develop a Serene Koi Pond</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cultivate a picturesque koi pond, enhancing the ambiance of your garden with graceful fish. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401730/extras/koi.gif?t=1731790153\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Customizable Atmosphere</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Set the mood with soothing music and ambient sounds, or personalize your experience by adding your own music files (wav, ogg, mp3).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401730/extras/atmos.gif?t=1731790153\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Breathtaking Hot Spring Scenery</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy beautifully crafted scenes that transport you to the heart of Japan\u2019s most tranquil hot springs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401730/extras/view_small.gif?t=1731790153\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Customizable and Pre-Set Wallpapers</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from stunning pre-set scenes or create your own custom backgrounds to use as your desktop wallpaper</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Interactive Wish Lanterns</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Share your thoughts, wishes, and experiences with other players by sending floating lanterns across the waters.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Play Online with Friends  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You and your friends can gather together in the host member's garden, joining as a cat, a fish, or your own avatar.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" 